Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.43,0:00:45.44,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to the sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.19,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:58.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:58.91,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:07.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has faded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:07.25,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:12.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:12.42,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:18.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.55,0:01:18.09,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:23.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.14,0:01:23.43,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.68,0:01:25.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
