Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:39.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.53,0:01:39.95,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:45.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to lose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.07,0:01:45.41,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.30,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:06.10,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.43,0:02:06.10,Italics - Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.56,0:02:11.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
